<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="Dokumentasi REST API lengkap untuk mengintegrasikan layanan <%= settings.web_name %> ke bot atau aplikasi Anda.">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css?v=2">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.14.8/dist/cdn.min.js" defer></script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; height: 5px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #334155; border-radius: 10px; }
        .dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #475569; }

        /* Copy button */
        .code-block-wrapper { position: relative; }
        .copy-btn {
            position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: #94a3b8; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .copy-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.13); color: #e2e8f0; }
        .copy-btn.copied { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.2); color: #10b981; border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.3); }

        /* Category tabs */
        .cat-tab { transition: all 0.2s; }
        .cat-tab.active-nokos { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#25d366,#128c7e); color:#fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -6px rgba(37,211,102,0.4); }
        .cat-tab.active-app   { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f43f5e,#e11d48); color:#fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -6px rgba(244,63,94,0.4); }
        .cat-tab.active-panel { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#3b82f6,#2563eb); color:#fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -6px rgba(59,130,246,0.4); }
        .cat-tab.active-script{ background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f59e0b,#d97706); color:#fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px -6px rgba(245,158,11,0.4); }

        /* Sidebar nav active */
        .snav-item.snav-active { color: #60a5fa; font-weight: 800; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.08); }
        .snav-item { transition: all 0.15s; }

        /* Endpoint badge */
        .badge-get  { background:#d1fae5; color:#065f46; }
        .badge-post { background:#dbeafe; color:#1e40af; }
        .dark .badge-get  { background:rgba(16,185,129,0.15); color:#6ee7b7; }
        .dark .badge-post { background:rgba(59,130,246,0.15); color:#93c5fd; }

        /* Table */
        .param-table td, .param-table th { padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.12); }
        .param-table th { font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: #64748b; }
        .param-table .req { color: #f43f5e; font-weight: 700; font-size: 11px; }
        .param-table .opt { color: #64748b; font-size: 11px; }
        .param-table .mono { font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; color: #60a5fa; font-size: 12px; }

        /* Highlight alert box */
        .info-box { border-left: 3px solid; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
        .info-box.blue  { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.07);  border-color: #3b82f6; color: #60a5fa; }
        .info-box.green { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.07);  border-color: #10b981; color: #34d399; }
        .info-box.amber { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.07);  border-color: #f59e0b; color: #fbbf24; }
        .info-box.red   { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.07);   border-color: #ef4444; color: #f87171; }

        [x-cloak] { display: none !important; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#F4F7FA] dark:bg-[#0B0D14] text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 antialiased min-h-screen" x-data="docsApp()" x-init="init()">

    <!-- Top Nav -->
    <nav class="bg-white/90 dark:bg-[#0E1020]/90 backdrop-blur-xl border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 sticky top-0 z-50 h-16">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-full flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <!-- Mobile hamburger -->
                <button @click="mobileOpen = !mobileOpen" class="lg:hidden p-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 rounded-xl transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/></svg>
                </button>
                <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
                    <img src="<%= settings.web_logo %>" alt="Logo" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-xl object-contain">
                    <span class="font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg"><%= settings.web_name %> <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium text-sm">API Docs</span></span>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <!-- Dark/Light toggle -->
                <button onclick="document.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark'); localStorage.setItem('theme', document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark')? 'dark':'light')"
                        class="p-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 rounded-xl transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z"/></svg>
                </button>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs font-black transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0">Dashboard →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Toast -->
    <div id="toast-container" class="fixed top-20 right-4 z-[9999] flex flex-col gap-2"></div>

    <!-- Mobile Sidebar Overlay -->
    <div x-show="mobileOpen" @click="mobileOpen = false" x-transition.opacity class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/60 z-40 lg:hidden" x-cloak></div>

    <!-- Layout -->
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)]">

        <!-- ===== SIDEBAR ===== -->
        <aside :class="mobileOpen ? 'translate-x-0' : '-translate-x-full'"
               class="fixed top-16 left-0 h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] w-72 z-50 bg-white dark:bg-[#0E1020] border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-6 overflow-y-auto transition-transform duration-300 lg:translate-x-0 lg:static lg:block lg:w-64 lg:shrink-0">

            <!-- Category Switcher -->
            <div class="mb-6">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Kategori API</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                    <button @click="setCategory('nokos')" class="cat-tab flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-black text-left transition-all"
                            :class="activeCategory === 'nokos' ? 'active-nokos' : 'text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white'">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12.004 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12c0 1.73.44 3.36 1.21 4.79L2 22l5.37-1.39c1.4.74 2.99 1.16 4.63 1.16 5.52 0 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12.004 2z"/></svg>
                        <span>Nokos OTP</span>
                    </button>
                    <button @click="setCategory('app')" class="cat-tab flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-black text-left transition-all"
                            :class="activeCategory === 'app' ? 'active-app' : 'text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white'">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                        <span>Premium App</span>
                    </button>
                    <button @click="setCategory('panel')" class="cat-tab flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-black text-left transition-all"
                            :class="activeCategory === 'panel' ? 'active-panel' : 'text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white'">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"/></svg>
                        <span>Panel Pterodactyl</span>
                    </button>
                    <button @click="setCategory('script')" class="cat-tab flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 rounded-xl text-xs font-black text-left transition-all"
                            :class="activeCategory === 'script' ? 'active-script' : 'text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white'">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
                        <span>Script / Digital</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 pt-5">
                <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Navigasi</p>
                <ul class="space-y-0.5 text-xs" id="sidebar-nav">
                    <!-- populated by JS per category -->
                    <template x-for="item in sidebarItems" :key="item.id">
                        <li>
                            <a :href="'#' + item.id"
                               @click="mobileOpen = false"
                               class="snav-item flex items-center justify-between px-3 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-bold text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-white/5"
                               :class="activeSection === item.id ? 'snav-active' : ''">
                                <span x-text="item.label"></span>
                                <span x-show="item.method" class="text-[9px] font-black uppercase px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md"
                                      :class="item.method === 'GET' ? 'badge-get' : 'badge-post'" x-text="item.method"></span>
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </template>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Base URL -->
            <div class="mt-6 p-3 bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/3 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 rounded-xl">
                <p class="text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-1">Base URL</p>
                <code class="text-xs text-blue-400 font-mono break-all"><%= settings.web_domain %>/api/v1</code>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- ===== MAIN CONTENT ===== -->
        <main class="flex-1 overflow-hidden px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 py-10 max-w-4xl">

            <!-- Hero Header -->
            <div class="mb-12" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div x-show="activeCategory === 'nokos'" x-cloak class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#25d366]/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#25d366]" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12.004 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12c0 1.73.44 3.36 1.21 4.79L2 22l5.37-1.39c1.4.74 2.99 1.16 4.63 1.16 5.52 0 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12.004 2zm5.72 14.15c-.24.68-1.2 1.24-1.65 1.29-.41.05-.95.07-1.54-.12-.36-.12-.83-.28-1.42-.53-2.52-1.07-4.14-3.66-4.26-3.82-.12-.16-1.02-1.37-1.02-2.61s.64-1.85.87-2.1c.24-.24.52-.3.69-.3h.49c.16.01.37-.06.58.45.21.52.73 1.79.79 1.91.06.12.1.26.02.42-.08.16-.18.26-.29.4-.12.13-.25.3-.36.42-.12.14-.25.29-.1.54.14.24.64 1.07 1.38 1.73.95.85 1.74 1.11 1.99 1.23.25.12.39.1.53-.06.14-.16.6-1.04.76-1.25.16-.21.32-.18.54-.1.22.08 1.4.66 1.64.78.24.12.4.18.46.28.06.1.06.58-.18 1.26z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-[#25d366]/70">Virtual OTP API</span>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Nokos OTP</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div x-show="activeCategory === 'app'" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4" x-cloak>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-rose-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-rose-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-rose-400/70">Streaming & Apps</span>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Premium App</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div x-show="activeCategory === 'panel'" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4" x-cloak>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-blue-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-400/70">Pterodactyl Panel</span>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Panel Pterodactyl</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div x-show="activeCategory === 'script'" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4" x-cloak>
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-amber-500/15 flex items-center justify-center">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-400/70">Bot & Digital Tools</span>
                        <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Script / Digital</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium text-base leading-relaxed" x-text="categoryDesc"></p>
            </div>

            <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
                 SHARED: Auth + Payment Types
            ════════════════════════════════════ -->
            <section id="auth" class="mb-12 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 pt-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-xl bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Authentication</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-5">Semua request wajib menyertakan API key di header. Generate API key di halaman profil reseller Anda.</p>
                <div class="code-block-wrapper bg-slate-900 dark:bg-[#0A0C18] rounded-2xl p-5 border border-slate-800 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
                    <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
                    <pre class="text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><span class="text-slate-500">// Headers wajib untuk setiap request</span>
{
  <span class="text-blue-400">"x-api-key"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"AOC-YOUR_SECRET_KEY_HERE"</span>,
  <span class="text-blue-400">"Content-Type"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"application/json"</span>
}</pre>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
                 NOKOS OTP SECTION
            ════════════════════════════════════ -->
            <div x-show="activeCategory === 'nokos'" x-cloak class="space-y-12">

                <!-- Get Services -->
                <section id="nokos-services" class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 pt-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                        <span class="badge-get text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-md">GET</span>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">/api/v1/nokos/services</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-5">Dapatkan daftar semua layanan OTP aktif beserta harga dan ID layanan yang dibutuhkan untuk order.</p>
                    <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Response</h4>
                    <div class="code-block-wrapper bg-slate-900 dark:bg-[#0A0C18] rounded-2xl p-5 border border-slate-800 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
                        <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Copy</button>
                        <pre class="text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto">{
  <span class="text-blue-400">"success"</span>: <span class="text-purple-400">true</span>,
  <span class="text-blue-400">"count"</span>: <span class="text-orange-400">4</span>,
  <span class="text-blue-400">"data"</span>: [
    {
      <span class="text-blue-400">"id"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"prod_abc123"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"name"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"WhatsApp OTP"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"otpServiceId"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"whatsapp"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"price"</span>: <span class="text-orange-400">1500</span>,       <span class="text-slate-500">// Harga per nomor (termasuk margin)</span>
      <span class="text-blue-400">"isActive"</span>: <span class="text-purple-400">true</span>
    },
    {
      <span class="text-blue-400">"id"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"prod_def456"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"name"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"Telegram OTP"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"otpServiceId"</span>: <span class="text-green-400">"telegram"</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"price"</span>: <span class="text-orange-400">1200</span>,
      <span class="text-blue-400">"isActive"</span>: <span class="text-purple-400">true</span>
    }
  ]
}</pre>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Get Countries / Rates -->
                <section id="nokos-rates" class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 pt-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                        <span class="badge-get text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-md">GET</span>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white">/api/v1/nokos/rates/:serviceId</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm font-medium mb-5">Ambil daftar negara dan operator yang tersedia untuk layanan OTP tertentu, beserta harga per operator.</p>
                    <div class="info-box blue mb-5">💡 <strong>serviceId</strong> = nilai field <code>otpServiceId</code> dari endpoint <code>GET /nokos/services</code>, contoh: <code>whatsapp</code></div>
                    <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Path Parameter</h4>
                    <table class="w-full param-table mb-5">
                        <thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Tipe</th><th>Wajib</th><th>Keterangan</th></tr></thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td class="mono">serviceId</td><td class="italic text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">String</td><td class="req">Ya</td><td>ID layanan OTP (whatsapp, telegram, google, dll)</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <h4 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2">Response</h4>
                    <div class="code-block-wrapper bg-slate-900 dark:bg-[#0A0C18] rounded-2xl p-5 border border-slate-800 dark:border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
